    "act1": "On Snowy Peaks Island, jagged mountains rise through endless blizzards, where a towering yeti-monkey Viking roams the frozen ridges. Wielding an icy axe and driven by the will of Doctor Krit, it raids anything that dares cross its path. At the highest peak lies the Frost Core, pulsing with ancient power. Romy, we must reach it, shatter its influence, and free the yeti monkey from Krit's control before the storm swallows the island whole.",
    "act2": "Suddenly, from above, a yeti-monkey Viking slides down an icy slope, swinging an axe made of glistening ice. It's clearly puzzled by the mathematics of its own weather patterns and starts unwittingly causing chaos!",
    "act3": "Your mission, Romy, is to restore order by solving the pattern conundrums created by the bungling yeti-monkey. In return, you'll claim the magical Frost Bracelet!",
    "goal": "Romy, master every math trial, reach the island's core in time, and break Doctor Krit's hold."
